This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and generation. The paper also involves geometric exaggeration, which falls under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. The use of GANs suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of landmark space and image space suggests that the paper may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
